%N A039091 Numbers whose base-9 representation has the same number of 2's and 3's.
%H A039091 Chris R. Rehmann, <a href="/A039091/b039091.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%t A039091 Select[Range[0, 29211], DigitCount[#, 9, 2]==DigitCount[#, 9, 3]&] (* _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 16 2026 *)
%o A039091 (MATLAB) x = 0:29211; d = dec2base(x,9)-'0'; a = x(sum(d==2,2)==sum(d==3,2)); disp(regexprep(num2str(a), ' +', ', ')) % _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 16 2026
